instructions: In a large pot over medium heat, heatcoconut oil. Add onion, bell pepper, and carrots and cook until tender, 6 to 8minutes. Add garlic and stir until fragrant, 1 minute. Add curry powder and cayenneand season with salt. Stir until combined.Pour over coconut milk and chickenbroth and bring to a simmer. Add shredded chicken, cilantro, and ramen noodlesand cook until noodles are al dente.Garnish with cilantro and serve withlime.

steps.step: In a large pot over medium heat, heatcoconut oil.
Add onion, bell pepper, and carrots and cook until tender, 6 to 8minutes.
Add garlic and stir until fragrant, 1 minute.
Add curry powder and cayenneand season with salt. Stir until combined.
Pour over coconut milk and chickenbroth and bring to a simmer.
Add shredded chicken, cilantro, and ramen noodlesand cook until noodles are al dente.
Garnish with cilantro and serve withlime.
